task_input.question: Compose a poem - a poem about a haircut! But lofty, noble, tragic, timeless, full of love, treachery, retribution, quiet heroism in the face of certain doom! Six lines, cleverly rhymed, and every word beginning with the letter s!

o3-mini-high-effort-poem_9.task_output:
Sovereign shears swiftly slice sumptuous, silken strands, shorn.  
Sincere suitor, sorrow‐stricken, sinks; soulful solitude, sworn.  
Subversive schemer surreptitiously sabotages sweet symmetries, shorn.  
Stalwart sentinel stands, subduing shadowed storms, sworn.  
Savage strife strikes; scarred spirits surge, shorn.  
Sacrificial, steadfast, soulful—summoning strength, subduing suffering’s siege, sworn.
